# RETRO

This is a set of extensions for RRE.

# I/O Extensions

# Console Input

~~~
{{
  'io:Keyboard var
  :identify
    @io:Keyboard n:zero? [
      #1 io:scan-for dup n:negative?
      [ drop 'IO_DEVICE_TYPE_0001_NOT_FOUND s:put nl ]
      [ !io:Keyboard ] choose ] if ;
  ---reveal---
  :c:get (-c) identify @io:Keyboard io:invoke ;
}}
~~~

